FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774379485
OL,3,CMother of missing toddler calls fake
OL,4,Cimage 'heartbreaking and sick'
OL,6,FBen, from Sheffield, disappeared on
OL,7,Fthe Greek island of Kos 34 years ago,
OL,8,Faged 21 months.
OL,10,FDespite one of the longest missing
OL,11,Fperson investigations in British
OL,12,Fhistory - including two excavations at
OL,13,Fthe farmhouse where he was last seen -
OL,14,Fhis whereabouts remain unknown.
OL,16,FThe fake post showed Ben as an adult,
OL,17,Fusing an age-progressed photo, with a
OL,18,Fchild, sitting next to Kerry claiming
OL,19,Fan "emotional face to face chat."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1774379485
OL,3,CMother of missing toddler calls fake
OL,4,Cimage 'heartbreaking and sick'
OL,6,FKerry told Calendar she'd reported it
OL,7,Fto South Yorkshire Police - describing
OL,8,Fit as "heartbreaking and sick."
OL,10,FA number of people have made unfounded
OL,11,Fclaims that they could be Ben in the
OL,12,F34 years since his disappearance.
OL,14,FThe most recent DNA test comes after
OL,15,Fthe social media page devoted to
OL,16,Ffinding Ben was contacted by the
OL,17,Fgirlfriend of a man allegedly bearing
OL,18,Fsimilarities to images of Ben. Ben's
OL,19,Ffamily are still awaiting the results
OL,20,Fof the test.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
